    <item>
      <title>黑石集团和 Ares 为 Odevo 签署 14 亿美元私人信贷协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/blackstone-ares-sign-1-4-billion-private-credit-deal-for-odevo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Ares Management Corp. 和 Blackstone Inc. 将联手为瑞典房地产管理公司 Odevo AB 提供价值 14.3 亿美元的私人信贷贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/blackstone-ares-sign-1-4-billion-private-credit-deal-for-odevo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔萨格称特朗普准备结束“大即坏”的并购观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-12/orszag-says-trump-poised-to-end-big-is-bad-view-of-m-a-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lazard Inc. 首席执行官 Peter Orszag 表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命的监管官员标志着拜登政府对并购的“大即坏”观点的终结。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上表示，进入 2025 年，交易环境“看起来非常有利”。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯将于周五发布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-12/orszag-says-trump-poised-to-end-big-is-bad-view-of-m-a-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:19:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国对冲基金创始人因涉嫌 13 亿美元税务诈骗在丹麦被判入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/british-hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-jailed-over-cum-ex-scam-in-denmark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对冲基金交易员桑杰·沙阿因策划了一起价值 10 亿美元的税务诈骗案被丹麦法官判处 12 年监禁，这是迄今为止欧洲庞大的 Cum-Ex 交易丑闻中判处的最重监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/british-hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-jailed-over-cum-ex-scam-in-denmark</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言明年加大财政支出以刺激消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/china-signals-more-fiscal-stimulus-rate-cuts-to-boost-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，2025年将增加公共借贷和支出，并将政策重点转向消费，以期在即将实施的美国关税威胁出口的情况下修复经济的薄弱环节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/china-signals-more-fiscal-stimulus-rate-cuts-to-boost-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 11:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员对“无人知晓”的中性利率进行冒险押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/neutral-rate-guessing-game-comes-with-high-stakes-in-bond-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的债券交易柜台，似乎每个人对中性利率都有自己的看法。中性利率是 3.3%。不，是 4.5%。实际上，是 2.4%。而且，一周五天，整天都在变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/neutral-rate-guessing-game-comes-with-high-stakes-in-bond-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据引发降息政策担忧，铜价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/metals-rise-before-outcome-of-china-s-top-economic-policy-meet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国初请失业金人数高于预期且生产者价格数据强劲，市场谨慎情绪蔓延，伦敦工业金属价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/metals-rise-before-outcome-of-china-s-top-economic-policy-meet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 04:53:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
